Package aas_core.aas3_0.types.impl

Class AdministrativeInformation

java.lang.Object
aas_core.aas3_0.types.impl.AdministrativeInformation
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAdministrativeInformation, IClass, IHasDataSpecification
public class AdministrativeInformation extends Object implements IAdministrativeInformation
Administrative meta-information for an element like version information.

Constraints:

  • Constraint AASd-005: If getVersion() is not specified then also getRevision() shall be unspecified. This means, a revision requires a version. If there is no version there is no revision neither. Revision is optional.

    • getTemplateId

      public Optional<String> getTemplateId()
      Description copied from interface: IAdministrativeInformation
      Identifier of the template that guided the creation of the element.

      In case of a submodel the IAdministrativeInformation.getTemplateId() is the identifier of the submodel template ID that guided the creation of the submodel

      The IAdministrativeInformation.getTemplateId() is not relevant for validation in Submodels. For validation the Submodel.getSemanticId() shall be used.

      Usage of IAdministrativeInformation.getTemplateId() is not restricted to submodel instances. So also the creation of submodel templates can be guided by another submodel template.

      Specified by:
      getTemplateId in interface IAdministrativeInformation
